 LinkedHashSet

 It is the child class of HashSet
 Introduces  in 1.4 version

 It is exactly same as HashSet except the following differences

 HashSet
 ==================
 The underlying datastructure is HashTable

 insertion order not preserved

 introduces in 1.2
 ===================
 LinkedHashSet
 ==================
 the underlying datastructer is
 hashtable + linked list

 insertion order is preserved

 introduced in 1.4 version

======================================

Note:

LikedHashSet is the best choice to develop cache based application ,
where duplicates are not allowed and insertion order must be preserved



